HEADWORD: Miscall
<hw>Mis*call"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To
call by a wrong name; to name improperly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To call by a bad name; to abuse.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Fuller.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

